Auto-Scaling

on-prem
Cloud -- PAYG --> 

7 AM - 10 AM --> 10000 users --> 100 servers - 3 hrs
10 AM - 1 PM --> 7000 users --> 70 servers
1 PM - 4 PM --> 20000 users --> 200 servers - 3 hrs
4 PM - 6 PM --> 5000 users --> 50 servers
6 PM - 11 PM --> 50000 users --> 500 servers - 5 hrs
11 PM - 7 AM (ND) --> 2000 users --> 20 servers

Auto-Scaling

Vertical auto-scaling --> scale up , scale down
Horizontal auto-scaling --> scale-out (increase), scale-in (decrease)
